      • modified

        boolean modified(Integer hashCode,
                 String command,
                 List<Object> args)
        Determine if a command might be operating on a modified key. Useful for, e.g., watch/multi.
        Parameters:
        hashCode - Hash code for the interested object.
        command - The redis command.
        args - Arguments to the command.
        Returns:
        true if the command would operate on a key that has been modified; false otherwise.
